TY  - JOUR
T1  - Blocks, Liquidity, and Corporate Control
AU  - Bolton, Patrick
AU  - Von Thadden, Ernst-Ludwig
Y1  - 1998/02/01
PY  - 1998
DA  - 1998/02/01
DO  - https://doi.org/10.1111/0022-1082.15240
T2  - The Journal of Finance
